### Accounts & Transactions — Manual HTTP Tests
### Run with VS Code REST Client or JetBrains HTTP Client
### Authenticate first using auth.http to get a valid session

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8003

### ── Dev dashboard (public, no auth required) ────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/dev
Accept: text/html

### ── Health check ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/up
Accept: text/html

### ── Accounts index (requires auth) ─────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Cookie: laravel_session=AUTHED_SESSION
Accept: text/html

### ── Accounts create page (requires auth) ────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/create
Cookie: laravel_session=AUTHED_SESSION
Accept: text/html

### ── Account detail page ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Replace {id} with a real account ID from the dev dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1
Cookie: laravel_session=AUTHED_SESSION
Accept: text/html

### ── Account detail page — non-member should return 403 ────────────────────
# Login as bob@demo.test who doesn't have access to a Globex account
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/999
Cookie: laravel_session=BOBS_SESSION
Accept: text/html

### ── Transaction create page ────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1/transactions/create
Cookie: laravel_session=AUTHED_SESSION
Accept: text/html

### ── Non-existent account — should return 404 ───────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/99999999
Cookie: laravel_session=AUTHED_SESSION
Accept: text/html

### ── Non-existent route — should return 404, NOT 500 ───────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/this-does-not-exist
Accept: text/html

### ── Dev seed action (Livewire) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# This tests the Livewire update endpoint directly
POST {{baseUrl}}/livewire-b5ad48da/update
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "components": []
}
